1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by year after year
of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
♪I can do nothing
but feign indifference♪

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,740
[Episode 30]

19
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:43,340
[Law Enforcement Office]

20
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,520
You've only got half an hour.

21
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,910
I'm late.

22
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,910
It's okay. It's not even a trial yet.

23
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,360
They can't do anything to me.

24
00:02:37,110 --> 00:02:38,190
How did you get in here?

25
00:02:41,110 --> 00:02:42,360
The warden here

26
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,520
owes me a favor.

27
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:54,260
♪Shrouded by year
after year of memories♪

28
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,670
Are you hungry?

29
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,720
I bring your favorite food.

30
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:06,260
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

31
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:08,620
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

32
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:13,820
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself.
Rebuild or crumble♪

33
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:14,320
Here.

34
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:16,470
Try it.

35
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:22,500
♪Driving away your dashing pretense♪

36
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:23,830
What's wrong?

37
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:28,510
The princess died right in front of me,

38
00:03:32,350 --> 00:03:33,840
but I couldn't save her.

39
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:42,060
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

40
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,000
I know.

41
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:47,550
She won't die in vain.

42
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,720
I'll have to

43
00:03:51,670 --> 00:03:53,630
settle this with that man
sooner or later.

44
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,240
Don't worry.

45
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,750
I'll definitely find a way
to get you out of here.

46
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,110
I believe in you.

47
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,720
Time's up.

48
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:24,780
♪It's okay to hold off on the romance♪

49
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:29,980
♪I'm not afraid of fights♪

50
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,000
Wait for me.

51
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:41,980
♪You're my only love in life♪

52
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:44,420
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

53
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:49,820
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself.
Rebuild or crumble♪

54
00:04:50,340 --> 00:04:52,380
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

55
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:58,300
♪Driving away your dashing pretense♪

56
00:04:58,540 --> 00:05:00,340
♪A drunken dream♪

57
00:05:03,110 --> 00:05:03,670
Wait for me.

58
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,350
Leave now.

59
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:17,540
♪I will still hold your hands tightly
and not let them go♪

60
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:31,260
[Grand Commandant's Residence]

61
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,550
The princess' suicide

62
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:37,350
puts the Yangs' only daughter
on a charge of murder.

63
00:05:39,350 --> 00:05:41,160
Master, you managed
to kill two birds with one stone.

64
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,270
How brilliant of you!

65
00:05:45,110 --> 00:05:46,600
That's what will happen

66
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,440
if she goes against me.

67
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:53,790
Master, why don't you
reveal Yang Caiwei's identity

68
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:56,200
and punish Pan Yue
for not reporting the fact

69
00:05:56,230 --> 00:05:57,550
and throw him into jail as well?

70
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,600
Back then,

71
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:05,480
although Yang Ji'an
was silently eliminated,

72
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,160
now there are still

73
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:11,040
many old officials

74
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:12,480
who have doubts about his case.

75
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,670
If they know
that his daughter is still alive,

76
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,600
I'm afraid
there will be another problem.

77
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,390
What's more,

78
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,880
although Pan Yue is not in jail,

79
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:29,390
he's like a caged beast

80
00:06:29,550 --> 00:06:30,950
without any help.

81
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:33,670
He's got no backing or power,
what is there to fear?

82
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,230
Keep an eye on Pan Yue.

83
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:45,950
If he dares take the plunge,

84
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:50,880
we'll have him

85
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,670
executed on the spot

86
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,920
in the name of justice.

87
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,830
It's you.

88
00:07:54,110 --> 00:07:55,070
What's the matter?

89
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,720
Could I ask you a favor?

90
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:01,880
Zuo Jingfei was around today,
so it's inappropriate to ask.

91
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,110
I'm listening.

92
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,230
I know

93
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:09,200
Miss Yang deserves to die

94
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,670
for being your enemy.

95
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:13,200
But we were in love before.

96
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,070
I would like to

97
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,040
see her for the last time at the trial.

98
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:30,600
You're just as nostalgic

99
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,910
as your father.

100
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:35,320
You can go and see her if you want.

101
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,000
Thank you, Master.

102
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:52,940
[Minister of Works' Residence]

103
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:26,840
You're finally back.

104
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,910
What happened?

105
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,440
Zhi may be unreasonable,

106
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,710
but

107
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:34,960
how could she kill someone?

108
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,910
There must be
some kind of misunderstanding.

109
00:09:38,230 --> 00:09:40,030
Do you have any idea how to save her

110
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,110
or

111
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,440
shall we ask the Empress for mercy?

112
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,110
It won't work.

113
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,520
Why do you say that?

114
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,590
Do you mean we just wait
for her to be decapitated?

115
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,230
Shangguan Zhi

116
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:01,960
is already dead.

117
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,280
Say that again.

118
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,030
Shangguan Zhi

119
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,790
is already dead.

120
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,200
Pan Yue,

121
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,080
do you remember

122
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,640
what you promised me

123
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:31,440
at my residence?

124
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,030
Now,

125
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:35,840
Zhi has committed
a terrible crime for you

126
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,840
and you just do nothing.

127
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:39,840
Are you even a man?

128
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:43,230
Pan Yue,

129
00:10:44,110 --> 00:10:46,710
how could I have been so blind

130
00:10:47,110 --> 00:10:49,080
to befriend someone like you?

131
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,280
Today,

132
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:53,280
I'm going to get even with you

133
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:54,840
on behalf of my sister!

134
00:10:57,100 --> 00:11:00,860
♪Even with great tact♪

135
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:04,780
♪How do you plan
for love and revenge?♪

136
00:11:06,110 --> 00:11:07,440
You won't fight back,

137
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,400
and you won't explain yourself.

138
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,590
You think

139
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,350
that makes me forgive you?

140
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:18,790
Do you believe I'll kill you right now?

141
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,230
I owe it to you.

142
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:33,640
You still won't save her, will you?

143
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:37,440
Fine.

144
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:39,960
I will.

145
00:11:40,710 --> 00:11:41,590
Shangguan Lan!

146
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:57,640
On the day of my wedding,

147
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,110
Shangguan Zhi

148
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,470
died in Heyang.

149
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:19,880
Ten years ago,

150
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,760
Yang Caiwei's father

151
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,670
was framed by the Jiang spies

152
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,520
and her whole family was killed.

153
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:29,960
Yang Caiwei's the only one who escaped.

154
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,350
All these years,

155
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:35,440
they've been searching for her.

156
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,080
They were planning

157
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:40,790
to kill her on my wedding day.

158
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,150
But no one expected

159
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:45,110
Shangguan Zhi

160
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,960
would abduct Yang Caiwei.

161
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,200
A woman died,

162
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:53,400
and her body has to be sent here.

163
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,150
How did she die?

164
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,230
She died of a broken heart.

165
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:09,110
In order to find out the clues
of the real culprit,

166
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:12,030
Yang Caiwei impersonated Shangguan Zhi
and came to my side.

167
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,470
We've just found out

168
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:16,320
the real identity of the mastermind,

169
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,320
but he set a trap

170
00:13:20,110 --> 00:13:21,200
before us.

171
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,960
Murder!

172
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,440
He used the princess's death

173
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,760
to frame Yang Caiwei

174
00:13:30,230 --> 00:13:31,960
and forced us
into a desperate situation.

175
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:37,200
This is the whole story.

176
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:41,080
I know everything is very unfair

177
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:42,400
to you.

178
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,840
But at the time,

179
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,590
we had no other choice.

180
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,080
I have preserved Shangguan Zhi's body

181
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,710
in an ice coffin in Heyang.

182
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,590
I was going to wait
for the truth to come to light

183
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:58,030
before I confessed everything to you

184
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,110
and asked for your forgiveness.

185
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,440
Listen.

186
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:17,110
I don't believe

187
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:22,550
any word you've said.

188
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:26,230
Impersonation?

189
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:28,910
Enemy and spies?

190
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,350
What's this got to do with Zhi?

191
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,080
You just don't want to save her.

192
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:44,880
Fine.

193
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:48,080
I'll save her.

194
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:15,110
There was an accident on the way here

195
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,280
and I fell,

196
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:18,590
but I'm glad I didn't miss
the auspicious time.

197
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:20,790
Zhi, are you okay?

198
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:21,790
Are you feeling better?

199
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:23,910
Who are you?

200
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:24,910
Stop kidding.

201
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:27,280
Zhi, I'm your elder brother.

202
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,400
Don't come any closer.
I'm not Shangguan Zhi.

203
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:31,200
What's wrong?

204
00:16:35,590 --> 00:16:36,840
I was going the wrong way.

205
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:40,710
Zhi.

206
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:42,670
This is Baocai.

207
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:44,280
Bao... Baocai.

208
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:45,760
But why are you so afraid of it?

209
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,670
I... I'm not...

210
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:34,050
Grand Commandant Jia, don't worry.

211
00:17:34,050 --> 00:17:35,160
Tomorrow's trial

212
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:37,000
will bring justice to the princess.

213
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,350
Mr. Pan, if you don't get out of here,

214
00:17:40,470 --> 00:17:41,560
we're going to have to
do something about it.

215
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:43,070
Wait.

216
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,430
I wondered who it was.

217
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:55,590
So it's Mr. Pan.

218
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,430
You're still worried about

219
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:01,680
the jailed Shangguan Zhi
at this point, huh?

220
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:03,560
Mr. Pan,

221
00:18:04,190 --> 00:18:06,560
you're really a loyal man.

222
00:18:10,710 --> 00:18:11,880
Anyway,

223
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,710
I didn't expect

224
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:16,560
Miss Shangguan,

225
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:18,350
who looks so weak

226
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,350
on the outside,

227
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,920
to be tougher than a man.

228
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:24,830
Indeed.

229
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,680
No matter how much I tortured her,

230
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:28,280
she just wouldn't fess up.

231
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,190
If I'd known,

232
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,430
I shouldn't have changed into

233
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:38,190
my new boots this morning.

234
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:40,880
I'll kill you!

235
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:41,560
Young Master!

236
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:45,520
Young Master!

237
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:47,400
Let go of me!

238
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,800
Don't be so rude.

239
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:58,350
If you hurt Mr. Pan,

240
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:00,560
Miss Shangguan will be heartbroken

241
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,760
before her demise.

242
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:05,640
Jia Quan, do you think
your scheme is brilliant?

243
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,680
If it is other officials to be
the presiding judge

244
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,000
rather than your henchmen,

245
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,760
Shangguan Zhi won't be convicted.

246
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:15,830
Is that so?

247
00:19:19,710 --> 00:19:21,430
Pan Yue.

248
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:24,280
Since you're so resentful,

249
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,830
it's fine.

250
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:38,110
I'll give you a chance.

251
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:40,950
I'll let you preside
over the trial tomorrow.

252
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:42,430
I'd like to see

253
00:19:43,230 --> 00:19:44,640
if you can speak so eloquently

254
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:47,040
when you're standing in the court

255
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:50,710
and interrogating your loved one.

256
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:32,980
♪Worshipping the dead♪

257
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:37,020
♪Boiling a pot of bitter wine♪

258
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:37,860
[Shuyu Abode]

259
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:41,020
♪As decades of spring and autumn pass♪

260
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:44,860
♪I watch the surges of unending waves♪

261
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:48,940
♪I wish upon you all that is well♪

262
00:20:49,060 --> 00:20:52,740
♪Let out a cry that ends all relations♪

263
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:57,140
♪Staying in
this boundless realm of purgatory♪

264
00:20:57,180 --> 00:21:01,700
♪Just to protect your tenderness♪

265
00:21:05,620 --> 00:21:07,180
[Law Enforcement Office]

266
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:10,820
♪How do you plan for love and revenge?♪

267
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:14,820
♪Longing turns to ashes,
ashes scatter to thin air♪

268
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:16,110
Bringing in the offender, Shangguan Zhi.

269
00:21:19,180 --> 00:21:22,820
♪Despite countless thoughts♪

270
00:21:23,180 --> 00:21:26,740
♪What should I do with my aching body?♪

271
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:31,180
♪Attracted by the setting moon
and refuse to leave♪

272
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:35,420
♪Don't forget the way you came♪

273
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:49,620
♪A bright heart worn by tragedies♪

274
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:04,040
Walk faster.

275
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,450
No ill-treatment to offenders.

276
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,830
Yes, sir.

277
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,640
Today's trial

278
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,880
is not going to be pleasant.

279
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,310
Are you afraid?

280
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:29,000
Pan Yue said he had a way.

281
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:31,920
The slightest hint of fear in me

282
00:22:32,170 --> 00:22:33,500
would be a distrust of him.

283
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,160
Your father

284
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:42,710
was just as brave

285
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:45,680
as you.

286
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,110
Maybe

287
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:50,920
he truly believed

288
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:53,110
in us as his buddies.

289
00:23:03,190 --> 00:23:03,880
You may go now.

290
00:23:11,780 --> 00:23:15,620
[Self-discipline
and official duties are paramount]

291
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:28,000
Eunuch Gao, Grand Commandant Jia
and Mrs. Jia have arrived.

292
00:23:45,430 --> 00:23:46,310
Pan Yue,

293
00:23:48,110 --> 00:23:49,430
Jing's been treating you well.

294
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:52,710
Don't let her down.

295
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:02,280
Since Mr. Pan

296
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:04,560
has agreed to preside over the trial,

297
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:06,520
he must know what he's doing.

298
00:24:07,430 --> 00:24:09,190
Don't worry, Darling.

299
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,040
Darling, this way, please.

300
00:24:34,420 --> 00:24:36,190
What kind of person
would do such a thing?

301
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:44,700
What a person.

302
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,630
Bring in the offender, Shangguan Zhi.

303
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:05,680
Here comes the offender.

304
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:06,520
She's here.

305
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:07,920
She's here.

306
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,310
Mr. Pan.

307
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:18,520
These are the questions
from the Empress.

308
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:22,350
Be sure to question the offender
word by word.

309
00:26:22,710 --> 00:26:25,040
Don't ask anything else

310
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:28,160
to avoid the suspicion
of compromising justice.

311
00:26:41,740 --> 00:26:44,740
[The Empress's Questions]

312
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,590
Shangguan Zhi,

313
00:26:57,800 --> 00:26:59,230
I've been ordered to hear

314
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:00,800
the case of the princess's death.

315
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:05,110
The Empress has some questions for you.

316
00:27:06,590 --> 00:27:07,350
The first question.

317
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:11,230
Pan Yue and the princess' wedding
was approaching,

318
00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:14,400
I heard you've been pestering Pan Yue.

319
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,520
What exactly

320
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,830
is your relationship with Pan Yue?

321
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,950
I didn't know Pan Yue was such a person.

322
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:33,110
I do admire Pan Yue,

323
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:36,110
but Pan Yue never gave me any promise.

324
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,230
It's all my imagination.

325
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:39,400
She's so shameless.

326
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:41,520
It takes two to tango.

327
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:52,110
Did Pan Yue know
about the incident at Fengya Garden?

328
00:27:52,950 --> 00:27:54,190
Did you conspire?

329
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:56,390
If you tell the truth,

330
00:27:57,110 --> 00:28:00,160
your family will be
exempted from punishment.

331
00:28:03,430 --> 00:28:04,470
I took it upon myself

332
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:06,470
to meet the princess.

333
00:28:06,710 --> 00:28:07,950
Pan Yue knew nothing about it.

334
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:14,190
Did you kill the princess for love?

335
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:17,880
What did the princess do to you

336
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,400
that made you

337
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,230
hate her so much?

338
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,070
No.

339
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:27,640
The princess was no inferior to men.

340
00:28:27,710 --> 00:28:28,640
I admired her.

341
00:28:28,710 --> 00:28:29,800
I've never hated her.

342
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:32,280
Again, I repeat myself.

343
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,470
I'm innocent.

344
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:36,430
The princess committed suicide.

345
00:28:38,190 --> 00:28:40,520
She's still denying
that she killed the princess.

346
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:43,470
Jing had always been so tough.
She wouldn't have committed suicide.

347
00:28:43,710 --> 00:28:45,400
You're not making any sense.

348
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,350
Shangguan Zhi,

349
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,430
you said the princess committed suicide.

350
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:04,470
Do you have any evidence?

351
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,590
The wound on the princess' chest

352
00:29:08,950 --> 00:29:11,040
was a self-inflicted wound
with a dagger in her right hand.

353
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:13,110
The angle was from top to bottom,

354
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:16,160
so the wound should be narrow
on the left and wide on the right.

355
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:17,680
An autopsy

356
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:20,070
will prove that my statement is true.

357
00:29:21,470 --> 00:29:22,520
You're full of nonsense.

358
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:25,000
According to the autopsy report,

359
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,710
the wound on the princess' chest
is a bloody mess

360
00:29:27,950 --> 00:29:29,800
caused by multiple stabbings.

361
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:32,230
Is this not an act of venting anger?

362
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,880
The body must have been tampered with

363
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,830
to cover up the suicide

364
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:40,800
and confuse the public.

365
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:43,800
Mr. Pan, an autopsy

366
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:47,110
to identify the wounds
and the cause of death

367
00:29:47,190 --> 00:29:48,470
will clear my name.

368
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:50,400
Do you still want to
desecrate Jing's body?

369
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,070
You wish!

370
00:29:53,450 --> 00:29:54,100
Mrs. Jia,

371
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:56,830
if a victim was stabbed while alive,

372
00:29:57,190 --> 00:30:00,110
the wound would be broad,
with the skin and bones exposed,

373
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,650
and the blood
would be visible in all areas.

374
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:03,860
But if a victim was stabbed after death,

375
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:06,610
the blood wouldn't stain the skin,
and the flesh would be dry and white.

376
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:08,710
If we can open the coffin
and examine the body,

377
00:30:09,530 --> 00:30:10,280
we can prove

378
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:12,760
that the princess committed suicide.

379
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,760
The other stab wounds

380
00:30:15,150 --> 00:30:16,520
were made after the death
of the princess

381
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:18,940
by someone who wanted to frame me.

382
00:30:29,430 --> 00:30:30,280
Fellow officials,

383
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:33,040
there's more to this case
than meets the eye.

384
00:30:34,430 --> 00:30:37,230
Should I go ahead with the judgment
in spite of the truth,

385
00:30:38,190 --> 00:30:39,950
or should I set a new date
for the trial?

386
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,950
Mr. Pan,

387
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:50,680
you've gone to great lengths

388
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:53,590
to get Shangguan Zhi off the hook.

389
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:54,560
I dare not.

390
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:58,880
I just don't want to let you down.

391
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:02,310
Report.

392
00:31:06,430 --> 00:31:07,190
Fellow officials,

393
00:31:07,430 --> 00:31:08,310
there's a man outside

394
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,110
saying he's a witness
to the murder of the princess.

395
00:31:10,470 --> 00:31:11,560
He asks to be summoned to the court.

396
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:13,920
He can prove
Shangguan Zhi's evil intentions

397
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:14,920
and conspiracy.

398
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,110
The only witness in Fengya Garden

399
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:21,800
is Sima Xuan.

400
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:25,400
How can there be other witnesses?
Deny him.

401
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,680
Let him in!

402
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,560
Yes.

403
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:54,640
Shangguan Lan,

404
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:57,000
