407
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:14,280
She's Yang Caiwei, the undertaker
of Coffin House in Heyang.

408
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,430
The real Shangguan Zhi

409
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:17,950
was killed by her long ago.

410
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:19,040
Ling...

411
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,430
Yang Caiwei?

412
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,230
Isn't it the daughter of Yang Ji'an

413
00:32:28,430 --> 00:32:31,590
that Mr. Pan married in Heyang
a few months ago?

414
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,000
Yang Caiwei,

415
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:38,760
you killed my sister

416
00:32:39,930 --> 00:32:40,730
and used witchcraft

417
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,040
to disguise yourself as her.

418
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,830
Do you admit to this?

419
00:32:49,710 --> 00:32:51,040
I'm a fake indeed,

420
00:32:52,070 --> 00:32:54,800
