505
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:48,140
I'm fine.

506
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:50,220
If my vital organs are hurt,

507
00:39:50,340 --> 00:39:51,940
I won't even have the strength
to talk to you.

508
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:54,140
I just didn't expect you

509
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:55,100
