510
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,220
Two centimeters to the lower left
of the Shenque acupoint.

511
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:00,780
Fortunately, I was stabbed here.

512
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,660
As long as it's treated in time,

513
