523
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:30,660
We've got too many
people involved this time.

524
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:33,460
We must bring down Jia Quan
as soon as possible,

525
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:35,180
or they'll all be implicated.

